# BIG Ideas

## Multiplayer
    Players play on the same board, attempting to salvage what they can with three stocks
    Choose Credit Score to race to {500, 750, 1000}
    Shields work to also bounce asteroids away (or potentially at another player)

## Campaign
    Banked "Credits" can be used to buy new ships - Lost if destroyed
    - Higher Yield on Salvage
    - Higher Yield on Asteroids
    - Stacks +1 Shield
    - Stacks +2 Shield
    - Smart Bomb to Clear Board
    - Smaller Hitbox Higher maneuverability
    - Smallest Hitbox Highest maneuverability
